edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner

Class TransportationEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.Event
      • edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.TransportationEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TransportationEvent
extends Event
    This class represents a Transportation Event of a vacation, which is one of the two subclasses of Event, and contains six fields, three of which are inherited from the Event class (name, date, and time). The three extra fields are event mode of travel, origin, and destination, which are traits specific to a transportation event
